    <description>SF-390 -  ETG Repository

Overview: Emerging Technology Group (ETG) - is a team with in-depth competitor knowledge, they provide support to field sales with “silver bullets” to close deals against competitor. Today field sale submit requests to the ETG team via google form; to allow scalability and SLA reporting we plan to utilize OOB Case functionalities. 

